<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Points for Selling Scrap</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F4F9F7; /* Soft light greenish background */
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Home link styles */
        .home-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #27AE60;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #F4F9F7;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 2px solid #27AE60;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .home-btn i {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .home-btn:hover {
            background-color: #27AE60;
            color: #FFF;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Main content section */
        .main-content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #27AE60;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .points-display {
            color: #27AE60;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #2C3E50;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .call-to-action {
            background-color: #27AE60;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .call-to-action:hover {
            background-color: #1e7a42;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .home-btn {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }

            .call-to-action {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/user/home" class="home-btn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Home</a>

    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>Your Points for Selling Scrap</h1>
        <div class="points-display">
            You currently have <%= points %> points.
        </div>

        <div class="info-text">
            Thank you for being a part of our eco-friendly community! Every scrap you sell helps the environment, and in return, you earn points. These points can be redeemed for exciting rewards and benefits.<br><br>
            <strong>Need more information?</strong><br>
            Feel free to reach out to us if you have any questions about the points system or need assistance with your account. We're here to help!<br><br>
            <strong>Call us at: <a href="tel:+917736628387" style="color: #27AE60; font-weight: 600;">+91 77366 28387</a></strong><br><br>
            Thank you for your continued support in making the world a cleaner, greener place!
        </div>

        <a href="/user/home" class="call-to-action">Learn More About How Points Work</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
